Label: License expression type name (content item)
Description: A short free-text name for a license expression type, when the code in <EpubLicenseExpressionType> provides insufficient detail – for example when a machine-readable license is expressed using a particular proprietary encoding scheme. Optional and non-repeating, and must be included when (and only when) the <EpubLicenseExpressionType> element indicates the expression is encoded in a proprietary way.
Format: <dd>Variable length text, suggested maximum length 100 characters</dd>
